prompt:
Nurse: Hi, this is Rachel calling from O'Connor Hospital. I'm an AI on a recorded line. Is this Paxton Winner?

Patient: Yeah.

Nurse: Thank you for confirming. Could you please provide your date of birth for verification purposes?

Patient: Yeah. November twenty fifth nineteen seventy one.

Nurse: Thank you for confirming, Ms. Winner. I'm calling about your upcoming total knee replacement. Is this a good time to talk?

Patient: Sure.

Nurse: Great, thank you for your time, Ms. Winner. I hope your day is going well so far. Can you share a bit about how you've been feeling today?

Patient: Oh, okay.

responses.gpt4: I'm glad to hear that you're okay, Ms. Winner. With the new knee, are there any activities you're looking forward to do that you've been unable to do?
responses.our_model: I'm sorry, Ms. Winner, I didn't quite catch that. Could you please share a bit about how your day has been going so far?
